Jeremy Clarkson, 62, and his girlfriend Lisa Hogan, 49, have been soaking up the sunshine for the past few weeks on a holiday getaway. The former Top Gear presenter shared a video of his partner, as the former model and actress performed an impressive backflip into the water on Wednesday. She put her toned physique on full display in a swimsuit as Lisa showed off her flexible skills in a candid video shared by Jeremy, in view of his 4.9 million followers. He captioned the post: "Just amazing. I mean she was born in the sixties." The video, which has been viewed over one million times, caused a stir with many of his fans commenting on the clip. Liam Potter joked: "Your turn. Same technique please." Michael commented: "Best backflip in the world," while Sasha added: "Simply... brilliant."